He has a &gt;50% win rate in all ELOs and 53-54% in Plat+. Its not like he has a negligible playrate either. He&#039;s been in 4/5 of my games today and the one he wasn&#039;t in he was banned.

Considering Draven is supposedly one of the higher skillcap champs in the game, something seems very off. His level 1 damage coupled with the rate at which he snowballs are out of control. Addressing that would be my suggestion.

